did.abstract: Includes surveys of graduates and records of the Cornell Office of Resident Instruction.

bioghist.head: ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY
bioghist.p: Prior to 1988, the office was known as Office of Resident Instruction. As of 1988, the name has been changed to the Office of Academic Programs.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Includes surveys of graduates and records of the Cornell Office of Resident Instruction.
